                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18341016-112-off608" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18341016-112-off608" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18341016-112-off608" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18341016-112-cd609" type="crimeDate">6th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341016-112-off608 t18341016-112-cd609"></join>, 1 jacket, value 6s.; 2 blankets, value 7s.; 1 rug, value 2s.; and three shirts, value 10s.
            </rs>; the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18341016-112-victim1060" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Birch
                  <interp inst="t18341016-112-victim1060" type="surname" value="Birch"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18341016-112-victim1060" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
